data.description: Great House! Great Land! Great Location! Nestled on 3 acres of land, including a fishing pond, in Caledonia School District, is this 4 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom Home Sweet Home. Beautifully landscaped, some additional updates, New Roof, New Gutters with transferable lifetime warranty, above ground pool, Tall ceilings with exposed beams in the living room, Open kitchen and dining room combination, and spacious bedrooms make this traditional ranch style house feel like home.
